led%20its%20March%20Madness%20contracts%20from%20New%20Jersey%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbetting-prediction-markets-kalshi-trump-election-sports-pop-culture-trading-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrediction%20markets%20have%20surged%20in%20popularity%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%202024%20US%20presidential%20election%20and%20companies%20including%20Kalshi%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FCrypto.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrypto.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20expanded%20into%20sports%20events.%20Sports%20predictions%20are%20similar%20to%20betting%20in%20that%20users%20can%20put%20money%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20game%2C%20but%20those%20contracts%20can%20be%20traded%20and%20typically%20only%20include%20whether%20a%20team%20will%20win%20or%20lose%20(rather%20than%20on%20player%20stats%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-flutter-fanduel-same-game-parlay-changed-us-sports-betting-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparlays%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20has%20driven%20over%20%24320%20million%20in%20trading%20volume%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20men's%20March%20Madness%20championship%20alone%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-addiction-warns-bettors-lose-money-march-madness-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarch%20Madness%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20US%20sports%20betting%20events%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20sports%20gambling%20is%20limited%20to%20the%2039%20US%20jurisdictions%20where%20it's%20been%20legalized%20and%20regulated%2C%20sports%20predictions%20from%20Kalshi%20are%20being%20offered%20in%20all%2050%20states.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-gambling-conference-next-summit-takeaways-ai-predictions-sweepstakes-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESports%20predictions%20are%20a%20major%20threat%20%E2%80%94%20and%20opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20for%20betting%20operators%2C%20some%20of%20which%20have%20expressed%20interest%20in%20predictions%20and%20are%20likely%20watching%20closely%20to%20see%20how%20Kalshi's%20regulatory%20battle%20plays%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20historical%20legal%20battle%20that%20pits%20states'%20traditional%20authority%20over%20gaming%20and%20sports%20betting%20against%20whether%20commodities%20exchanges%20regulated%20by%20the%20%5BCommodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%5D%20can%20include%20sports%20betting-like%20offerings%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Kilsby%2C%20chief%20analyst%20at%20Vixio%2C%20a%20regulatory%20tech%20company%20that%20works%20with%20the%20gambling%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2f1a9e8-d4b5-4b4c-b49c-7c9e5c00db10%5C%22%3EAll%20eyes%20are%20on%20Kalshi%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20has%20sued%20regulators%20in%20Nevada%20and%20New%20Jersey%20in%20response%20to%20the%20cease-and-desists.%20The%20company%20argued%2C%20in%20part%2C%20that%20Kalshi%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfederally%20regulated%20exchange%26quot%3B%20overseen%20by%20the%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%2C%20which%20has%20the%20sole%20authority%20to%20approve%20or%20reject%20its%20events%20contracts%2C%20per%20a%20March%2028%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20described%20the%20ways%20its%20sports%20contracts%20differ%20from%20betting%2C%20including%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20reflect%20a%20'bet'%20against%20the%20'house.'%26quot%3B%20(Contrary%20to%20that%20point%2C%20some%20states'%20sports%20betting%20laws%20cover%20peer-to-peer%20betting.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Kalshi%20argues%20that%20shutting%20down%20in%20Nevada%20and%20New%20Jersey%20could%20violate%20CFTC%20rules%20that%20its%20events%20contracts%20be%20open%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20courts%20and%20the%20CFTC%20decide%20Kalshi's%20sports%20contracts%20are%20legitimate%2C%20it%20could%20%26quot%3Btrigger%20a%20significant%20reaction%20from%20the%20sports%20betting%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Kilsby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20a%20scenario%20in%20which%20FanDuel%20and%20DraftKings%20don't%20ultimately%20want%20to%20move%20into%20that%20market%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you'll%20very%20quickly%20see%20more%20companies%20positioning%20themselves%20to%20launch%20sports%20exchange%20platforms%20under%20the%20CFTC%20guidelines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20saga%20will%20likely%20last%20several%20months%2C%20and%20other%20hurdles%20could%20emerge%2C%20legal%2C%20regulatory%2C%20and%20gambling%20insiders%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sports%20wagering%20industry%20is%20looking%20at%20this%20very%20carefully%2C%20and%20they're%20trying%20to%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andrew%20Kim%2C%20an%20appellate%20and%20gaming%20litigator%20at%20Goodwin.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20balancing%20act%20right%20now%20of%20not%20offending%20the%20regulators%20that%20oversee%20their%20prime%20product%20but%20also%20not%20missing%20out%20on%20an%20opportunity%20to%20jump%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20innovative%20gray%20areas%20that%20really%20formed%20%5Bdaily%20fantasy%20sports%5D%20and%20all%20the%20other%20sports%20wagering%20industries%20to%20begin%20with.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20states%20could%20oppose%20sports%20predictions%2C%20as%20could%20tribal%20groups%20with%20the%20authority%20to%20conduct%20gaming%20on%20many%20lands%20and%20exclusivity%20with%20some%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaming%20industry%20consultant%20Dustin%20Gouker%2C%20who%20broke%20the%20news%20about%20the%20New%20Jersey%20cease-and-desists%20through%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclosingline.substack.com%2Fp%2Fnj-cease-and-desist-kalshi-robinhood%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClosing%20Line%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20letters%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbellwether%20of%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20next.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESports%20predictions%20threaten%20revenue%20for%20states%20like%20Nevada%20and%20New%20Jersey.%20New%20Jersey%2C%20which%20led%20the%20expansion%20of%20legal%20sports%20betting%20in%20the%20US%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2Fnyregion%2Fnew-jerseys-appeal-of-sports-betting-ban-heads-to-supreme-court.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappealing%20a%20federal%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20brought%20in%20over%20%241%20million%20in%20sports%20wagering%20revenue%20in%20January%2C%20making%20it%20the%20third%20largest%20US%20market%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americangaming.org%2Fresources%2Fcommercial-gaming-revenue-tracker%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Gaming%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20also%20undermines%20states'%20control%20over%20what%20constitutes%20sports%20betting%20within%20their%20borders%20and%20what%20they%20do%20and%20do%20not%20allow.%20The%20matter%20could%20eventually%20end%20up%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20depending%20on%20where%20the%20lower%20courts%20and%20the%20CFTC%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20hard%20to%20ignore%20that%20this%20battle%20over%20the%20states'%20rights%20to%20regulate%20sports%20betting%20is%20coming%20at%20a%20key%20moment%20for%20the%20industry%3A%20March%20Madness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20cease-and-desist%20letters%2C%20New%20Jersey's%20Division%20of%20Gaming%20Enforcement%20pointed%20to%20the%20state's%20restrictions%20on%20betting%20on%20college%20sports.%20The%20state%20prohibits%20betting%20on%20college%20games%20that%20take%20place%20in%20the%20state%20or%20involve%20local%20teams%20like%20Rutgers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20states%20are%20looking%20to%20what%20happens%20here%2C%20and%20whether%20they're%20successful%2C%20and%20how%20Kalshi%20and%20Robinhood%20respond%2C%26quot%3B%20Gouker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMarch%2031%2C%202025%3A%20This%20story%20was%20updated%20to%20reflect%20additional%20details.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshis-sports-predictions-come-under-fire-amid-march-madness-trades-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743456544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb067763d72727e198c3f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshis-sports-predictions-come-under-fire-amid-march-madness-trades-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kalshi%20and%20Robinhood%20were%20handed%20cease-and-desists%20in%20New%20Jersey%20over%20their%20March%20Madness%20sports%20predictions.%20The%20outcome%20could%20change%20gambling.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arodriguez%40businessinsider.com%20(Ashley%20Rodriguez%2CMackenzie%20Meaney)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshis-sports-predictions-come-under-fire-amid-march-madness-trades-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tom%20Hardy%20Says%20Venom%20Crossover%20With%20Tom%20Holland%E2%80%99s%20Spider-Man%20%E2%80%98Got%20as%20Close%20as%20I%20Could%20Possibly%20Imagine%20Getting%E2%80%99%20Before%20Falling%20Apart%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743456319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236352970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tom%20Hardy%20appeared%20on%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Discourse%20Podcast%E2%80%9D%20from%20The%20Playlist%20and%20confirmed%20that%20a%20crossover%20between%20Venom%20and%20Tom%20Holland%E2%80%99s%20Spider-Man%20%E2%80%9Cgot%20as%20close%20as%20I%20could%20possibly%20imagine%20getting%E2%80%9D%20before%20falling%20apart.%20The%20Oscar%2