ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-submarines-17-billion-over-budget-in-crisis-lawmaker-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVirginia-class%20submarines%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20led%20to%20new%20developments%20in%20where%20and%20how%20the%20force%20can%20operate%2C%20stay%20hidden%2C%20and%20gather%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUUVs%20can%20extend%20the%20range%20at%20which%20the%20Navy%20can%20conduct%20missions.%20Their%20varying%20capabilities%20for%20surveillance%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20smaller%20size%2C%20mean%20that%20the%20Navy%20can%20deploy%20them%20to%20places%20that%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20reach%20with%20other%20assets.%20They%20are%20also%20attritable%20compared%20to%20more%20expensive%20submarines.%20There%20is%20potential%20in%20this%20tech%2C%20making%20fielding%20it%20of%20growing%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20challenges%20in%20this%2C%20but%20the%20Navy%20has%20seen%20success%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20ongoing%20deployment%20of%20the%20Virginia-class%20submarine%20USS%20Delaware%20in%20Europe.%20Gaucher%20said%20that%20the%20submarine%20had%20operated%20alongside%20a%20Huntington%20Ingalls%20Industries-made%20Remus%20UUV%20600%20in%20a%20Norwegian%20fjord%20for%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHII's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhii.com%2Fwhat-we-do%2Fcapabilities%2Funmanned-systems%2Fremus-uuvs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERemus%3C%2Fa%3E%20drones%20come%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20depths%2C%20mission%20durations%2C%20and%20speeds.%20They've%20seen%20commercial%20applications%20for%20ocean%20exploration%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaucher%20said%20that%20the%20Navy's%20approach%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20way%20Elon%20Musk's%20Space%20Exploration%20Technologies%20Corporation%2C%20or%20SpaceX%2C%20approaches%20rapid%20iterative%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20taking%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I'll%20call%20%5Bit%5D%20a%20SpaceX%20approach%20to%2C%20'Hey%2C%20get%20it%20out