C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eaae5369253ccddf9ac030%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222637%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pita%20was%20my%20favorite%20product%20in%20this%20set%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20fluffier%20and%20more%20flavorful%20than%20the%20store-bought%20pita%20and%20so%20fast%20and%20convenient%20to%20make.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20I%20baked%20the%20slow-fermented%20artisanal%20pita%2C%20which%20only%20took%20eight%20minutes%20in%20the%20oven%20(not%20much%20longer%20than%20toasting%20a%20piece%20of%20bread).%20I%20love%20the%20simplicity%20of%20this%20product%3A%20just%20whole%20wheat%20flour%2C%20bread%20flour%2C%20salt%2C%20water%2C%20yeast%2C%20and%20olive%20oil.%20This%20was%20the%20perfect%20pita%20for%20dipping%20in%20hummus%2C%20but%20I%20can%20also%20imagine%20using%20it%20for%20sandwiches.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7db9545-9289-4de8-9a5b-8d63ccc013e5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gluten-free%20options%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGluten-free%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223747%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Wildgrain%20gluten-free%20country%20loaf%20cooking%20in%20the%20oven.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ead3f369253ccddf9ac6eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20gluten-free%20country%20loaf%20was%20a%20standout%20among%20the%20Wildgrain%20products%20I%20tested.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20big%20fans%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20of%20Wildgrain's%20gluten-free%20products%20are%20made%20in%20a%20dedicated%20gluten-free%20facility%2C%20making%20them%20safe%20for%20people%20with%20Celiac%20disease.%20I%20selected%20the%20gluten-free%20country%20loaf%2C%20giant%20Snickerdoodle%20cookies%2C%20and%20cheese%20Tortellini.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnyone%20who's%20had%20gluten-free%20bread%20knows%20the%20slices%20are%20usually%20bland%2C%20comically%20small%2C%20and%20the%20texture%20too%20dry%20and%20crumbly.%20The%20Wildgrain%20country%20loaf%20yielded%20thick%20slices%20that%20had%20plenty%20of%20bubbles%20on%20the%20inside%20and%20golden%20crust%20on%20the%20outside.%20It's%20bursting%20with%20so%20much%20rich%2C%20subtly%20nutty%20flavor%2C%20that%20was%20delicious%20with%20a%20pat%20of%20butter%20alone%2C%20but%20it%20also%20made%20a%20phenomenal%20canvas%20for%20my%20avocado%20toast.%20The%20only%20downside%20is%20that%20this%20bread%20takes%20some%20forethought.%20It%20has%20to%20bake%20for%2028-32%20minutes%20and%20then%20cool%20for%20another%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223527%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gluten-free%20country%20loaf%20cut%20to%20show%20the%20interior%20from%20Wildgrain%20Subscription.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eaba6363d72727e198b49c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20gluten-free%20bread%20from%20Wildgrain%20was%20soft%20and%20chewy%20with%20a%20crisp%20crust.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cheese%20tortellini%20was%20also%20a%20major%20success.%20Gluten-free%20pasta%20tends%20to%20cook%20too%20quickly%2C%20resulting%20in%20overly%20soft%2C%20gluey%20noodles%20that%20stick%20together.%20That%20didn't%20happen%20with%20this%20tortellini%2C%20which%20cooked%20in%20boiling%20water%20for%20just%20three%20minutes.%20Thanks%20to%20a%20blend%20of%20four%20different%20cheeses%20stuffed%20inside%2C%20it%20had%20a%20complexity%20of%20flavor%20I%20haven't%20really%20experienced%20with%20other%20tortellini.%20The%20infusion%20of%20cracked%20black%20pepper%20into%20the%20pasta%20shell%20was%20a%20really%20nice%20touch.%3C%2Fs