nd%20is%20bursting%20with%20flavor%3F%20Sign%20us%20up.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20definitely%20recommend%20Wildgrain%20for%20anyone%20who%20loves%20fresh%20bread%2C%20artisanal%20pastries%2C%20and%20hand-cut%20pasta%20but%20doesn't%20have%20time%20to%20make%20them%20or%20doesn't%20live%20near%20a%20great%20bakery.%20Plus%2C%20the%20gluten-free%20options%20are%20delicious%20and%20far%20better%20than%20any%20I've%20tried%20from%20my%20local%20grocery%20stores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20drawbacks%20to%20Wildgrain%20are%20the%20cost%20per%20item%20and%20the%20need%20for%20freezer%20space.%20That%20said%2C%20Wildgrain's%20breads%2C%20pastas%2C%20and%20pastries%20are%20good%20in%20the%20freezer%20for%20up%20to%20a%20year%2C%20so%20I%20can%20stock%20up%20without%20worrying%20about%20food%20waste.%20Although%20these%20products%20are%20more%20pricey%20than%20what%20I'm%20used%20to%20buying%2C%20I'm%20happy%20to%20pay%20extra%20for%20stellar%20taste%2C%20texture%2C%20variety%2C%20and%20convenience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fwildgrain-box-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743452406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eae63669253ccddf9acb76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fwildgrain-box-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20ate%20Wildgrain's%20bake-from-frozen%20pita%20bread%2C%20cookies%2C%20gluten-free%20tortellini%2C%20and%20more.%20Here's%20why%20the%20subscription%20box%20deserves%20your%20freezer%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Strong)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fwildgrain-box-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2