Wilmore%20thanked%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20SpaceX%20owner%20Elon%20Musk%20for%20their%20help%20in%20bringing%20them%20back%20from%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%2C%20where%20they%20stayed%20on%20for%20nine%20months%20after%20their%20Boeing%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20malfunctioned%2C%20turning%20a%20mission%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20short%20into%20a%20long%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20astronauts%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20Fox%20News%20said%20space%20flight%20is%20hard%2C%20and%20using%20new%20technology%20to%20try%20to%20further%20and%20better%20themselves%20is%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Boeing%20%26quot%3Bscrewed%20this%20up%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Wilmore%20said%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20point%20fingers%20at%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20In%20certain%20respects%2C%20we%20were%20stuck.%20In%20certain%20respects%2C%20maybe%20we%20were%20stranded.%20But%20based%20on%20how%20they%20were%20couching%20this%2C%20that%20we%20were%20left%20and%20forgotten%20and%20all%20that%2C%20we%20were%20nowhere%20near%20any%20of%20that%20at%20all.%20So%20stuck%2C%20okay%2C%20we%20didn't%20get%20to%20come%20home%20the%20way%20we%20planned.%20So%20in%20one%20definition%2C%20we're%20stuck.%20But%20in%20the%20big%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20we%20weren't%20stuck.%20We%20planned%20and%20trained%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wilmore%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20said%20they%20prepped%20as%20if%20they%20were%20going%20to%20stay%20long%20while%20planning%20for%20the%20short%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20mission%2C%20the%20Starliner%20portion%20of%20the%20mission%2C%20first%20flights%2C%20test%20flight.%20And%20that%20was%20our%20focus%2C%20but%20we%20trained%20for%20everything.%20Maintenance%20on%20station%2C%20science%20on%20station%2C%20spacewalks%20on%20station%2C%20robotics%2C%20arm%20work%20on%20station.%20We%20trained%20for%20it%20all.%20And%20we%20were%20prepared%20to%20do%20anything%20that%20we%20were%20asked%20of%20for%20a%20long%20duration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20planning%20for%20one%20thing%2C%20preparing%20for%20other.%20And%20that's%20not%20unique%20to%20us.%20This%20is%20what%20a%20human%20space%20flight%20programme%20does.%20This%20is%20what%20each%20individual%2C%20the%20army%20that%20supports%20human%20space%20flight...%20that%20is%20passionate%20about%20human%20space%20flight...%20do.%20We%20plan%20for%20as%20many%20contingencies%20as%20we%20can%20dream%20up%20because%20this%20is%20a%20hard%20business.%20It's%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wilmore%20indicated%20it%20would%20be%20absolutely%20wrong%20to%20pin%20blame%20on%20anyone%20for%20what%20happened%20with%20their%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20There%20are%20many%20questions%20that%20as%20the%20commander%20of%20CFT%20(crew%20flight%20test)%2C%20I%20didn't%20ask.%20So%20I'm%20culpable.%20I'll%20admit%20that%20to%20the%20nation.%20There's%20things%20that%20I%20did%20not%20ask%20that%20I%20should%20have%20asked.%20I%20didn't%20know%20at%20the%20time%20I%20needed%20to%20ask%20them.%20But%20in%20hindsight%2C%20the%20signal%2C%20some%20of%20the%20signals%20were%20there.%20Is%20Boeing%20to%20blame%3F%20Are%20they%20culpable%3F%20Sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20NASA%20to%20blame%3F%20Are%20they%20culpable%3F%20Sure.%20Everybody%20has%20a%20piece%20in%20this%20because%20it%20did%20not%20come%20off.%20There%20were%20some%20shortcomings%20in%20tests%2C%20shortcomings%20in%20preparation%20that%20we%20did%20not%20foresee.%20So%20yeah%2C%20are%20there%2C%20could%20you%20point%20fingers%3F%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20point%20fingers.%20I%20hope%20nobody%20wants%20to%20point%20fingers.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20look%20back%20and%20say%2C%20shame%2C%20shame%2C%20shame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20look%20forward%20and%20say%2C%20let's%20rectify%20what%20we've%20learned%20and%20let's%20make%20the%20future%20even%20more%20productive%20and%20better.%20That's%20the%20way%20that%20I%20look%20at%20it.%20I%20think%20the%20way%20the%20nation%20should%20look%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wilmore%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20NASA%20Crew-9%20astronauts%20returned%20to%20Earth%20on%20SpaceX's%20Dragon%20capsule%20on%20March%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20alleged%20his%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden%20abandoned%20the%20astronauts%20in%20space.%20On%20March%207%2C%20he%20announced%20he%20gave%20permission%20to%20Mr%20Musk%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20two%20American%20astronauts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743445680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ftlaif9qg_sunita-butch_625x300_31_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-boeing-screw-up-sunita-williams-and-butch-wilmore-say-8056409%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA%20astronauts%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20thanked%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20SpaceX%20owner%20Elon%20Musk%20for%20their%20help%20in%20bringing%20them%20back%20from%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%2C%20where%20they%20stayed%20on%20for%20nine%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Release%20Epstein%20files'%20demand%20grows%20stronger%20after%20victim%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20claims%20she's%20dying%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743444475000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119819217%2Cimgsize-18478.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frelease-epstein-files-demand-grows-stronger-after-victim-virginia-giuffre-claims-shes-dying%2Farticleshow%2F119819155.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D