MK%20insists%20that%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20three-language%20policy%20is%20based%20on%20this.%20The%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20the%20party%20has%20alleged%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20enforce%20a%20cultural%20homogenization%20that%20will%20rob%20India%20of%20its%20diversity%20and%20the%20southern%20states%20of%20their%20distinct%20cultural%20identity.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20has%20argued%20that%20its%20current%20two-language%20formula%20-%20Tamil%20and%20English%20--%20serves%20it%20well%20and%20underscored%20that%20it%20is%20the%20second-largest%20contributor%20to%20the%20country's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20argued%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20%C2%A0has%20a%20bouquet%20of%20languages%20other%20than%20Hindi%20for%20the%20third%20option%20and%20insisted%20that%20it%20does%20not%20force%20a%20student%20to%20study%20Hindi.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20maintained%20that%20the%20third%20language%20will%20help%20people%20travelling%20to%20other%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%2C%20another%20BJP-ruled%20state%2C%20meanwhile%20plans%20to%20offer%20additional%20optional%20languages%20including%20Bengali%2C%20Marathi%2C%20Telegu%2C%20Tamil%20Gujarati%20and%20Punjabi%20in%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20an%20ambitious%20plan%2C%20there%20is%20no%20word%20on%20faculty%20recruitment%20or%20on%20minimum%20enrolment%20required%20to%20roll%20this%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInder%20Singh%20Parmar%2C%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20said%20this%20will%20bring%20about%20%26quot%3Ba%20hub%20of%20linguistic%20diversity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20has%20kept%20up%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20funds%20withheld%20for%20not%20accepting%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20system%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20number%20one%20in%20India.