as%20killed%20by%20Aurangzeb%20during%20the%20succession%20battle%20that%20saw%20the%20youngest%20of%20the%20four%20brothers%20take%20over%20the%20throne%20of%20Shah%20Jahan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743432780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fdntbm56_aurangzeb-tomb-security_625x300_18_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funnecessary-rss-leader-bhaiyyaji-joshi-on-controversy-over-aurangzebs-tomb-8055123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controversy%20over%20the%20tomb%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20is%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Suresh%20%26quot%3BBhaiyyaji%26quot%3B%20Joshi%2C%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funnecessary-rss-leader-bhaiyyaji-joshi-on-controversy-over-aurangzebs-tomb-8055123%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20still%20'working%20with%20US'%20after%20Trump%20says%20he%20is%20'angry'%20with%20Putin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743432618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fb5ce%2Flive%2F51488c90-0e35-11f0-bfea-d170975f1d6a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczd31157m31o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20its%20first%20response%20to%20Trump's%20criticism%20of%20Putin%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20tried%20to%20play%20down%20the%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A134%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczd31157m31o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczd31157m31o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczd31157m31o.am