e-125033100759_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20a%20company%20filing%2C%20the%20rights%20issue%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20163.1%20per%20share%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20premium%20of%20Rs%20158.1%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20US%20To%20Jointly%20Design%2C%20Manufacture%20Nuclear%20Reactors%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20moment%20for%20the%20India-US%20civil%20nuclear%20deal%2C%20which%20was%20signed%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20the%20US'%20Department%20of%20Energy%20or%20DoE%20has%20given%20the%20final%20approval%20permitting%20a%20US%20company%20to%20jointly%20design%20and%20build%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20overall%20framework%20of%20the%20India-US%20civil%20nuclear%20agreement%20was%20signed%20back%20in%202007%20by%20then%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20then%20US%20president%20George%20W%20Bush%2C%20it%20has%20taken%20nearly%2020%20years%20of%20negotiation%2C%20detailed%20discussions%2C%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20clearances%2C%20technology%20permits%2C%20liability%20clauses%2C%20and%20fine-tuning%20of%20blueprints%20to%20finally%20get%20the%20green%20signal%20to%20execute%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'BIG%20WIN'%20FOR%20INDIAN%20DIPLOMACY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20now%2C%20under%20the%20India-US%20civil%20nuclear%20deal%2C%20US%20firms%20could%20export%20nuclear%20reactors%20and%20equipment%20to%20India%2C%20but%20forbid%20them%20from%20any%20design%20work%20or%20manufacturing%20of%20nuclear%20equipment%20in%20India.%20New%20Delhi%20had%20remained%20firm%20that%20everything%20-%20from%20design%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20transfer%20of%20technology%20-%20had%20to%20be%20done%20in%20India.%20Successive%20governments%20stood%20firm%20by%20this.%20Now%2C%20after%20many%20years%2C%20and%20Russia%20gaining%20ground%2C%20US%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20terms%20set%20by%20New%20Delhi.%20US%20and%20Indian%20firms%20will%20now%20jointly%20manufacture%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors%20or%20SMRs%20and%20co-produce%20all%20its%20components%20and%20parts%20as%20well.%20This%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20big%20win%20for%20Indian%20diplomacy.%20The%20approval%20was%20given%20on%20March%2026%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20US%20has%20set%20one%20condition%20-%20that%20these%20jointly-designed%20and%20manufactured%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20be%20re-transferred%20to%20any%20other%20entity%20or%20end%20user%20in%20India%20or%20to%20other%20countries%20except%20the%20United%20States%20without%20the%20prior%20written%20consent%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commercial%20potential%20for%20civil%20nuclear%20energy%20in%20India%20is%20massive%2C%20the%20US%20government%20said%2C%20as%20the%20Department%20of%20Energy%20approved%20Holtec%20International's%20proposal%20to%20be%20granted%20specific%20authorisation%20with%20respect%20to%20restrictive%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulation%20which%20got%20the%20approval%20was%20the%2010CFR810%20-%20which%20is%20part%20810%20of%20title%2010%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Federal%20Regulations%20of%20the%20US%20Atomic%20Energy%20Act%2C%201954.%20It%20pertains%20to%20the%20DoE's%20%26quot%3Bstatutory%20responsibility%20for%20authorizing%20the%20transfer%20of%20unclassified%20nuclear%20technology%20and%20assistance%20to%20foreign%20atomic%20energy%20activities%20within%20the%20United%20States%20or%20abroad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBased%20on%20Holtec%20International's%20application%2C%20the%20authorization%20permits%20the%20company%20to%20transfer%20%26quot%3Bunclassified%20small%20modular%20reactor%20(SMR)%20technology%26quot%3B%20to%20three%20Indian%20firms.%20These%20include%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELarsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Limited%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETata%20Consulting%20Engineers%20Ltd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHoltec's%20regional%20subsidiary%20Holtec%20Asia.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOLTEC%20INTERNATIONAL%20-%20A%20GLOBAL%20LEADER%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS-based%20Holtec%20International%2C%20a%20global%20energy%20firm%2C%20is%20owned%20and%20promoted%20by%20Indian-American%20entrepreneur%20Krishna%20P%20Singh.%20Its%20fully-owned%20Asia%20subsidiary%20-%20Holtec%20Asia%20-%20has%20been%20operating%20since%202010%20and%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Pune%2C%20where%20it%20also%20runs%20its%20specialised%20engineering%20division.%20It%20also%20has%20its%20manufacturing%20plant%20in%20Gujarat's%20Dahej%2C%20located%20in%20Bharuch%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoltec%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20exporters%20of%20nuclear%20technology%2C%20components%2C%20and%20parts.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20the%20decommissioning%20sector%2C%20which%20ensures%20the%20safe%20and%20environmentally-responsible%20removal%20of%20industrial%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHoltec%20International%20had%20also%20sought%20approvals%20for%20two%20Indian%20government-owned%20firms%20which%20provide%20electricity%20to%20the%20end-users%2C%20and%20a%20government%20regulator%20for%20ensuring%20safety%20norms.%20These%20corporations%20were%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENuclear%20Power%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited%20or%20NPCIL%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENational%20Thermal%20Power%20Corporation%20or%20NTPC%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAtomic%20Energy%20Review%20Board%20or%20AERB%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20however%2C%20had%20not%20provided%20the%20required%20clearances%20for%20these%20state-owned%20corporations%20since%20Holtec%20had%20not%20yet%20got%20approval%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Energy.%20Now%20that%20it%20has%20got%20the%20nod%20from%20the%20US%20government%2C%20it%20will%20likely%20appeal%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20grant%20permits%20for%20these%20key%20Indian%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECOMPETITION%20WITH%20CHINA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20agreement%20between%20Washington%20and%20New%20Delhi%2C%20to%20jointly%20design%20and%20manufacture%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20in%20India%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20transfer%20of%20technology%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20massive%20diplomatic%20achievement.%20This%20is%20because%20it%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20is%20looking%20to%20boost%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20US%20and%20heavily%20promote%20'made-in-USA'%20equipment%20globally.%20At%20such%20a%20time%2C%20nuclear%20reactors%20being%20made%20in%20India%20shows%20a%20big%20gain%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20is%20also%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20win%20for%20India's%20private%20sector%2C%20which%20will%20gain%20specialisation%20and%20expertise%20in%20designing%20and%20manufacturing%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20-%20something%20that%20till%20now%20was%20only%20under%20the%20domain%20of%20government%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20which%20currently%20has%20expertise%20in%20smaller%20nuclear%20reactors%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20220MWe%20PHWR%20or%20Pressurised%20Heavy%20Water%20Reactors%2C%20will%20now%20get%20technology%20to%20build%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20with%20more%20advanced%20technology%20of%20PWRs%20or%20Pressurised%20Water%20Reactors.%20Most%20of%20the%20nuclear%20plants%20globally%20run%20on%20this%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20India-US%20move%20also%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20China%20is%20scaling%20up%20its%20plans%20to%20lead%20globally%20in%20the%20Small%20Modular%20Reactor%20(SMR)%20space%20by%20competitive%20pricing.%20Affordable%20SMRs%20are%20a%20key%20requirement%20for%20the%20Global%20South%20to%20progress%20in%20a%20cost-effective%20way%2C%20and%20both%20India%20and%20China%20are%20competing%20with%20each%20other%20in%20their%20outreach%20to%20the%20Global%20South.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743430200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ft2184cpk_modi-trump-india-us-nuclear-reactor-joint-manufacturing_625x300_31_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-us-to-jointly-design-manufacture-nuclear-reactors-in-india-8054762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20landmark%20moment%20for%20the%20India-US%20civil%20nuclear%20deal%2C%20which%20was%20signed%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20the%20US'%20Department%20of%20Energy%20or%20DoE%20has%20given%20the%20final%20approval%20permitting%20a%20US%20company%20to%20jointly%20design%20and%20build%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-us-to-jointly-design-manufacture-nuclear-reactors-in-india-8054762%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20stocks%20tumble%20on%20Trump%20tariff%20worries%2C%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20falls%20to%20lowest%20since%20September%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743429560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119810088%2Cimgsize-46034.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-stocks-tumble-on-trump-tariff-worries-sp-500-falls-to-lowest-since-september%2Farticleshow%2F119810082.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119810082.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-stocks-tumble-on-trump-tariff-worrie