alay%2C%20one%20of%20the%20worst-affected%20cities%20and%20the%20country's%20second-largest%2C%20with%20more%20than%201.7%20million%20inhabitants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20so%20dire%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20express%20what%20is%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aung%20Myint%20Hussein%2C%20chief%20administrator%20of%20Mandalay's%20Sajja%20North%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20camped%20out%20in%20the%20streets%20across%20Mandalay%20for%20a%20third%20successive%20night%2C%20either%20unable%20to%20return%20to%20ruined%20homes%20or%20nervous%20about%20the%20repeated%20aftershocks%20that%20rattled%20the%20city%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20had%20tents%20but%20many%2C%20including%20young%20children%2C%20simply%20bedded%20down%20on%20blankets%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20roads%2C%20trying%20to%20keep%20as%20far%20from%20buildings%20as%20possible%20for%20fear%20of%20falling%20masonry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junta%20said%20Monday%20the%20death%20count%20has%20risen%20to%202%2C056%2C%20with%20more%20than%203%2C900%20people%20injured%20and%20270%20still%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20Chinese%20nationals%20are%20among%20the%20dead%2C%20China's%20state%20media%20said%2C%20along%20with%20two%20French%20people%2C%20according%20to%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2019%20deaths%20have%20been%20confirmed%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20away%20in%20Thailand's%20capital%20Bangkok%2C%20where%20the%20force%20of%20the%20quake%20caused%20a%2030-storey%20tower%20block%20under%20construction%20to%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20communications%20down%20in%20much%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20true%20scale%20of%20the%20disaster%20has%20yet%20to%20emerge%20and%20the%20death%20toll%20is%20expected%20to%20rise%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Outdoor%20hospital%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandalay's%201%2C000-bed%20general%20hospital%20has%20been%20evacuated%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20patients%20being%20treated%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatients%20lay%20on%20gurneys%20in%20the%20hospital%20car%20park%2C%20many%20with%20only%20a%20thin%20tarpaulin%20rigged%20up%20to%20shield%20them%20from%20the%20fierce%20tropical%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelatives%20did%20their%20best%20to%20comfort%20them%2C%20holding%20hands%20or%20waving%20bamboo%20fans%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%2C%20very%20imperfect%20condition%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20medic%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20do%20what%20we%20can%20here.%20We%20are%20trying%20our%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sticky%20heat%20has%20exhausted%20rescue%20workers%20and%20accelerated%20body%20decomposition%2C%20which%20could%20complicate%20identification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20traffic%20began%20returning%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20Mandalay%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20restaurants%20and%20street%20vendors%20resumed%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20Muslims%20gathered%20outside%20a%20destroyed%20mosque%20in%20the%20city%20for%20the%20first%20prayer%20of%20Eid%20al-Fitr%2C%20the%20holiday%20that%20follows%20the%20Islamic%20fasting%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Humanitarian%20crisis%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20facing%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20country%20of%20more%20than%2050%20million%20people%20were%20immense%20even%20before%20the%20earthquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar%20has%20been%20ravaged%20by%20four%20years%20of%20civil%20war%20sparked%20by%20a%20military%20coup%20in%202021%2C%20with%20its%20economy%20shattered%20and%20healthcare%20and%20infrastructure%20badly%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20declared%20the%20quake%20a%20top-level%20emergency%20as%20it%20urgently%20sought%20%248%20million%20to%20save%20lives%20and%20prevent%20disease%20outbreaks%20over%20the%20next%2