in%20Pakistan%20are%20a%20result%20of%20a%20fallout%20between%20these%20two%20terror%20groups%2C%20intelligence%20operatives%20said.%20Terror%20financier%20Qari%20Abdu%20Rehman%2C%20a%20relative%20of%20India's%20most%20wanted%20terrorist%20Hafiz%20Saeed%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20unknown%20gunmen%20in%20Karachi%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-01%2Fhafiz-saeed-reuters_650x400_41514803412.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20officials%20who%20are%20looking%20into%20recent%20infiltration%20attempts%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Kathua%20have%20identified%20the%20terrorists%20as%20belonging%20to%20JeM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNATO%20weapons%20were%20recovered%20from%20them%2C%20including%20M4A1%20assault%20rifles%20and%20Glock%20handguns%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20intelligence%20operative%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20North%20Atlantic%20Treaty%20Organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20LeT%20terrorists%2C%20weapons%20recovered%20from%20them%20were%20either%20of%20Pakistan%20Ordnance%20Factories%20or%20Chinese-made%2C%20sources%20said.%20Of%20the%20approximately%20120%20terrorists%20hiding%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%2095%20per%20cent%20are%20foreigners%20and%20all%20have%20allegiance%20with%20JeM%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20widening%20rift%20between%20these%20two%20terrorist%20groups%20is%20useful%20for%20Indian%20security%20agencies%20operating%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%20In%20a%20recent%20case%2C%20the%20location%20of%20terrorists%20hiding%20in%20southern%20Kashmir%20was%20leaked%20by%20a%20rival%20group.%20In%20another%20case%2C%20a%20man%20kidnapped%20by%20the%20LeT%20later%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20JeM%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20reworking%20its%20strategies%20and%20operations%20due%20to%20these%20new%20dynamics%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20officer%20told%20NDTV%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Jaish%20was%20pushed%20out%20by%20%5BPervez%5D%20Musharraf%2C%20they%20operated%20along%20the%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20border%2C%20but%20mainly%20remained%20confined%20to%20Nuristan%20and%20Kunar%20provinces%20of%20Afghanistan.%20After%20Imran%20Khan%20came%20to%20power%2C%20they%20were%20allowed%20to%20enter%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%2C%20who%20monitors%20this%20region%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJaish%20has%20increased%20its%20presence%20around%20Bhawalpur%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20That%20marked%20the%20point%20when%20the%20rift%20between%20Lashkar%20and%20Jaish%20began%20to%20widen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20adding%20despite%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20trying%20to%20broker%20peace%20between%20the%20two%20terror%20groups%2C%20both%20have%20started%20targeting%20each%20other%20openly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20end%20the%20rivalry%20that%20is%20affecting%20the%20internal%20dynamics%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20their%20army%20is%20providing%20the%20terrorists%20a%20safe%20passage%20to%20cross%20over%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20doubling%20of%20infiltration%20attempts%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-05%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-army-generic-reuters_650x400_81525620118.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorists%20are%20sneaking%20into%20India%20from%20tunnels%2C%20riverine%20areas%2C%20and%20by%20cutting%20fences%2C%20a%20police%20officer%20said.%20The%20terrorists%20infiltrate%20into%20India%20with%20bare%20minimum%20logistics.%20They%20fi