20the%20right%20approach.%20But%20today%2C%20even%20they%20have%20accepted%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20them%20and%20say%20that%20better%20late%20than%20never%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Mr%20Tharoor%20nor%20the%20Congress%20have%20reacted%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20this%20latest%20kerfuffle%20involving%20Mr%20Tharoor%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20magazine%20article%20-%20'Covid's%20silver%20lining%20for%20India'%20-%20published%20Sunday%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fcolumns%2Fshashi-tharoor%2F2025%2F03%2F29%2Fcovids-silver-lining-for-india.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20India's%20'vaccine%20diplomacy'%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20the%20shipments%20enhanced%20our%20country's%20global%20image%20(and)%20India's%20efforts%20were%20appreciated%2C%20enhancing%20its%20reputation%20as%20a%20responsible%20global%20leader.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20didn't%20name%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20but%20he%20praised%20leadership%2C%20writing%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20India's%20vaccine%20diplomacy%20embodied%20and%20contributed%20to%20the%20very%20spirit%20of%20its%20soft%20power...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20remark%20has%20been%20met%20with%20delight%20from%20a%20BJP%20camp%20already%20prepping%20for%20next%20year's%20election%20-%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%20rejected%2C%20and%20quite%20thoroughly%2C%20its%20advances%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20ask%20anyone%20around%20the%20world%2C%20they%20will%20agree%20India%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20provided%20commendable%20assistance%20to%20small%20nations%20during%20Covid%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BEgg%20On%20My%20Face%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader's%20comments%20on%20'vaccine%20diplomacy'%20followed%20a%20'confession'%20this%20month%20-%20that%20he%20had%20been%20left%20with%20%26quot%3Begg%20on%20my%20face%26quot%3B%20after%20criticising%20India's%20position%20on%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-jubilant-congress-silent-over-shashi-tharoors-egg-on-face-comment-7960326%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20Jubilant%2C%20Congress%20Silent%20Over%20Tharoor's%20%26quot%3BEgg%20On%20Face%26quot%3B%20Note%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Raisina%20Dialogues%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20wiping%20the%20egg%20off%20my%20face...%20I%20was%20one%20of%20those%20who%20criticised%20India's%20position...%20it%20turns%20out%20I%20was%20wrong.%20India%20now%20has%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20can%20hug%20the%20President%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20of%20Russia...%20and%20still%20be%20accepted%20in%20both%20places...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-in-kerala-criticises-shashi-tharoor-for-praising-left-government-7729003%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECongress%20In%20Kerala%20Criticises%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20For%20Praising%20Left%20Govt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%2C%20well-meant%20though%20it%20may%20have%20been%2C%20kicked%20up%20a%20storm%20with%20the%20Congress%20taking%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20praise%20for%20its%20fierce%20rival.%20And%20that%20it%20followed%20apparent%20praise%20for%20Kerala's%20ruling%20Left%20Front%2C%20the%20Congress'%20state%20rival%2C%20led%20to%20speculation%20Mr%20Tharoor%20could%20switch%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'The%20Tougher%20Negotiator'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20praise%20for%20Mr%20Modi%20being%20labelled%20the%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20tougher%20negotiator%26quot%3