%20feed%20is%20probably%20filled%20with%20dreamy%2C%20hand-painted%20visuals%20labelled%20%E2%80%9CGhibli-style%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94from%20celebrities%20to%20everyday%20users%2C%20everyone%20seems%20to%20be%20trying%20it.%20But%20what%20exactly%20is%20Ghibli%2C%20and%20why%20has%20it%20taken%20over%20the%20internet%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20story%20behind%20Ghibli%20art%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudio%20Ghibli%20was%20founded%20in%20Japan%20on%20June%2015%2C%201985%2C%20by%20legendary%20animators%20Hayao%20Miyazaki%20and%20Isao%20Takahata%2C%20along%20with%20producer%20Toshio%20Suzuki.%20The%20studio%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20%E2%80%9CGhibli%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20Italian%20word%20for%20a%20hot%20desert%20wind%2C%20symbolising%20its%20mission%20to%20bring%20a%20fresh%20breeze%20to%20the%20animation%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20new%20version%20of%20the%20OpenAI%20chatbot%20ChatGPT%20lets%20users%20transform%20their%20personal%20images%20into%20Ghibli-style%20anime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20studio%E2%80%99s%20influence%20extends%20far%20beyond%20Japan%2C%20inspiring%20generations%20of%20artists%20and%20animators%20worldwide.%20Its%20films%20are%20known%20for%20their%20rich%20storytelling%2C%20breathtaking%20visuals%2C%20and%20deep%20themes%20exploring%20nature%2C%20identity%2C%20and%20human%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20commercial%20success%2C%20Ghibli%20is%20revered%20for%20its%20meticulous%20hand-drawn%20animation%2C%20use%20of%20watercolor%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20philosophical%20depth%20that%20resonates%20with%20audiences%20of%20all%20ages.%20The%20studio%20is%20known%20for%20its%20strong%2