%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-98-1743258327.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-98-1743258327.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-98-1743258327-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-98-1743258327-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-98-1743258327-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-98-1743258327-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417017%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20hatchery%20requires%20monitoring%2024%2F7%2C%20for%20which%20volunteers%20take%20turns.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20early%20March%2C%20the%20hatchlings%20start%20emerging%2C%20and%20this%20continues%20until%20late%20May.%20Unlike%20the%20night%20patrols%2C%20hatchery%20work%20is%20more%20demanding.%20%E2%80%9CTurtle%20walks%20are%20very%20romantic%20but%20the%20hatchery%20is%20like%20a%20maternity%20ward%2C%20requiring%20more%20dedication%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteers%20monitor%20the%20hatchery%20round%20the%20clock%2C%20checking%20for%20emerging%20hatchlings%20every%20two%20hours.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20hatchlings%20are%20out%2C%20you%20also%20need%20to%20dig%20out%20and%20remove%20the%20rotten%20eggs%2C%20which%20is%20smelly%20work%20and%20not%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20hatchlings%20are%20ready%2C%20they%20are%20released%20into%20the%20sea.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20we%20have%20had%20800%20to%201000%20people%20waiting%20to%20say%20bye%20to%20j